    <p class="font-size-14">We are excited to join the Rackspace family, and are confident this will allow us to offer the absolute best cloud management experience possible, for everyone. We will continue to support multiple clouds, and our users can expect to receive the same, high level of service.</p>
    <div><a href="/blog" class="strong">Blog post</a> | <a href="/acquisition-faq" class="blue">Acquisition FAQ</a> | <a href="/free-basic-checks" class="blue">NEW: Free basic monitoring!</a> | <a href="/getting-started" class="blue">How to get started</a> | <a href="http://jobs.rackspace.com/search?q=%22san+francisco%22" class="blue" target="_blank">We're hiring</a></div>
