  <div id="sidebar">
    
      <h3>Announcements</h3>
      <ul>
        
          <h4>Share your Graphs</h4>
          
          <p>We've enabled permalinks in graphs so you can link and share them with your colleagues.</p>
          
        
          <h4>Custom Alerts</h4>
          
          <p>Design your own custom alerts by setting parameters that meet your needs; innovation at work!</p>
          
        
          <h4>Automatic DNS</h4>
          
          <p>When a new node comes online, you can have Cloudkick automatically create a DNS record that makes sense. Helps ops teams to automatically keep up-to-date records for all the servers they manage.</p>
          
        
          <h4>Alert History</h4>
          
          <p>Performance overview of what servers and monitors in your infrastructure are the most noisy (or quiet) to see yours: Dashboard / Monitor tab / Alert History sub-tab.</p>
          
        
      </ul>
    
  </div><!--/#sidebar-->

